(1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">&ldquo;TRANSPARENCY AND AUTHENTICITY &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">THAT&rsquo;S WHY IGC IS DIFFERENT THAN OTHERS&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">IGC: Impact Global Consultant aims to provide authentic support to aspiring students to pursue higher education overseas that best matches their requirements and areas of interest</span></p>', '1725531961_snow-sports-720px.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">IGC aims to guide students in finding the most suitable course at the right university or college for their higher studies. We see ourselves fulfilling every student\'s ambitions in their chosen field. And IGC: Impact Global Consultant is committed to maintaining transparency and integrity to ensure student files get a successful Visa outcome.</span></p>', '1725532755_water-boarding-720px.jpg', '<p>Whatever study abroad assistance you need,<br>IGC provides the holistic support to help you study in<br>USA, UK, Canada, Australia, and Europe</p>', '1725533082_pexels-italo-melo-2379004(1).jpg', '<p>IGC strives to help students to reach their desired country, assisting them in every step of completing a study permit application and even after that. We try to build a lifelong relationship with students and make their study overseas dream into reality. We are a professional education consultant offering expertise in bridging prospective students and leading universities\' programs.</p>', '1725533329_about-extreme-sports-1.jpg', '<p>1. Complete guidance on Course Selection, Financial Documentation, SOP Writing, and Visa Application<br>2. After Visa support, settlement in abroad, finding job abroad, and build everlasting connection<br>3. Provide solution for every query related to education abroad</p>', '1725533551_about-extreme-sports-2.jpg', '1', NULL, '2024-09-30 10:56:31');

