: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Degrees with Distinction: Your Belgian degree will be recognized and respected worldwide, giving you a competitive edge in the global job market.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Quality of Life Unmatched: Belgium embraces a healthy work-life balance. Imagine cycling through picturesque canals, indulging in world-class chocolate, and cheering on your favorite football team in lively pubs. Belgium offers a fulfilling life beyond academics.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Master the Master\'s:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span 