: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Visa Procedures: Apply for the appropriate student visa type well in advance. Prepare documents like proof of acceptance, financial means, and health insurance. (Link to Belgian official information on visas:</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://www.schengenvisainfo.com/belgium/visa/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://www.schengenvisainfo.com/belgium/visa/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">https://www.schengenvisainfo.com/belgium/visa/</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbs