e=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Find the right visa: Different visas apply depending on your program and intended stay. The</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://www.nyidanmark.dk/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://www.nyidanmark.dk/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc; background: white; mso-highlight: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">New to Denmark</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">website will guide you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Gather visa documents: Proof of acceptance, financial means, travel insurance, and health documents might be required. Check the SIRI website for specifics.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Attend your visa interview: Be prepared to answer questions about your study plans and financial support.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_l4y2mxoi4p7b\"></a><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Moving Mountains (or Suitcases):</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Book your accommodation: Start early, as finding housing in Denmark can be tricky. Explore student dorms, private rentals, or shared apartments.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Arrange travel: Book your flights well in advance, especially during peak season. Research visa requirements for any transit countries.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Pack smart: Think layers for unpredictable weather, practical clothing for cycling (a Danish must!), and essentials like adapters and medication.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_dpa1x5nz2scq\"></a><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Bonus Tip: Brush up on some basic Danish phrases. It\'ll go a long way in endearing yourself to the locals!</span></em></h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_ihexm4dcpwtw\"></a><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Life in Denmark: A Hyggelig Adventure</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Welcome to Hygge Land! Danish life is a tapestry woven with cozy comfort, stunning scenery, and a vibrant social scene. Prepare for:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Hygge: This concept goes beyond cozy candles and blankets. It\'s about cherishing simple pleasures, good company, and creating a warm, inviting atmosphere. Think fika breaks with cinnamon rolls, board game nights with friends, and picnics in sun-dappled parks.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Cycling Culture: Embrace the two-wheeled life! Denmark is a cyclist\'s paradise, with dedicated lanes, safe infrastructure, and a bike-friendly attitude. Ditch the car and join the pedal-powered throngs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Nature\'s Playground: From rugged coastlines and pristine beaches to rolling hills and fairytale forests, Denmark is an outdoor enthusiast\'s dream. Hike, kayak, camp, or simply soak in the fresh air - nature is always at your doorstep.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Cosmopolitan Delights: Danish cities are buzzing with creativity. Explore art galleries, sample Michelin-starred cuisine, or catch a concert in a converted church. You\'ll never be short of things to do.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Social Harmony: Danes are known for their friendly, laid-back nature. Feel welcome to join conversations, ask for directions, or strike up friendships. The \"lagom\" philosophy (not too much, not too little) permeates everyday life, creating a peaceful and harmonious atmosphere.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_9ay7tswbxhwc\"></a><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Why Denmark is Perfect for Every Student, Even Vikings in Training</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">So, even if your academic background hasn\'t been Valhalla-worthy, Denmark welcomes you with open arms. Here\'s why it\'s the perfect fit:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Supportive Learning Environment: Danish universities prioritize student well-being and academic success. Expect small class sizes, personalized attention, and access to academic support services.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Focus on Practical Skills: Danish education blends theoretical knowledge with practical application. Internships, projects, and hands-on learning are integral parts of many programs, giving you valuable real-world experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Second Chances and Lifelong Learning: Denmark\'s flexible education system allows you to switch programs or even universities if your interests evolve. You can also pursue further education throughout your life.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Global Opportunities: A Danish degree opens doors to international internships, study abroad programs, and careers with multinational companies. The world is your oyster!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Are you ready to trade Dhaka\'s honking horns for the melodic chirping of Copenhagen\'s bicycles? To swap stifling classrooms for vibrant, interactive learning spaces? To ditch rote memorization for hands-on problem-solving? Denmark beckons, Bangladeshi students, offering not just an education, but a transformative experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Picture yourself:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 12.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Standing atop Copenhagen\'s iconic Round Tower, the city unfurling beneath you like a vibrant tapestry.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Cycling through sun-dappled forests, the scent of pine needles filling your lungs.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Sipping a steaming cup of coffee in a cozy cafe, discussing philosophy with your Danish classmates.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Presenting your groundbreaking research at an international conference, your Bangladeshi pride shining through.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Landing your dream job at a world-renowned tech company, your Danish degree paving the way.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Denmark is not just a study destination, it\'s a launchpad for your dreams. So, don\'t just dream it, live it. Embrace the Viking spirit of adventure, chart your course to Denmark, and write your own epic saga of academic success and personal growth.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">Take the leap with</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc; background: white; mso-highlight: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">IGC</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">, Bangladeshi students. Denmark awaits!</span></p>', '1727865228_Why Denmark Should Be Your Study Valhalla, Bangladeshi Students! (1).png', '1', '2024-10-02 10:33:48', '2024-10-02 10:33:48', NULL);
