ndif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Proof of English-language proficiency (e.g., an IELTS or TOEFL certificate, for schools located in English-speaking countries) or any other language test</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Test results for admissions (e.g., GMAT/GRE scores, in graduate school)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Hopefully, you&rsquo;re planning to use some of these steps or prepare</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">In the coming few weeks, we&rsquo;ll be writing more tips &amp; strategies to help prepare your documents, fix goals about improving your productivity, overcome procrastination, and get a better focus.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Also, feel free to call us at : 01886 462211-14</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">So let&rsquo;s begin the journey of your study abroad with IGC.</span></p>', '1727868473_IGC-study-Abroad-guide (2).png', '1', '2024-10-02 11:27:53', '2024-10-02 11:27:53', NULL),
(9, 7, '2024-10-02', 'International Studies Abroad: How to choose right program through IGC: Impact Global Consultant', 'international-studies-abroad:-how-to-choose-right-program-through-igc:-impact-global-consultant', 'The opportunity to receive a world-class education, travel the world and make friends for life', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">The opportunity to receive a world-class education, travel the world and make friends for life are only a few of the advantages you can enjoy when you\'re an international college student. But, selecting which program to enroll in is vital to get the most out of your time abroad.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Whatever your passions and goals, there\'s a degree program to meet your needs. Then, it\'s just a matter of where you wish to study abroad.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">If you\'re confused by several options or aren\'t sure where you should begin, this guide can aid you in the process of making a decision.</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_5nd74kowtqu4\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">What\'s your key interest?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">You\'ll be studying this course over the next three to four years, so selecting the subject you are interested in is crucial. Besides the subject you\'re studying, you\'re more likely to succeed and enjoy the learning experience that will last for the rest of your life.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">If you have passions and hobbies outside of school, you might want to consider deciding your degree on them. You\'ll learn in-depth about the subjects you\'re interested in while acquiring the necessary skills to begin a professional career.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">What is your ideal job?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">The thought of what job you\'d like to pursue at the following university will help you choose the right degree.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Certain professionals, such as lawyers, doctors, and architects, must obtain specialist certifications before working. Thus, if you\'d like to work in a similar field, you\'ll have to follow a specific career path.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">The requirements for higher education for many other occupations are more flexible. Yet, looking at the most studied degrees studied by people working in the field you are interested in may give you some direction and direction.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">If you\'re not finding the perfect job yet, you shouldn\'t be worried. Instead, try taking the job or vocation test, which can aid you in finding a career that fits your abilities and character.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">It is also possible to remain flexible by selecting a flexible and transferable course such as management, economics, and managing. Employers highly value these subjects from a variety of sectors and industries.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_bcc5h1ff31xh\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">What is your expertise?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Knowing the areas where you excel can help narrow the options for your degree. Of course, each university program demands effort and dedication, but you\'ll be in good shape when you select an international study program that you are already employed.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">You\'re not only more likely to excel academically, but the results will help keep you focused throughout the long library hours and early-morning classes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">It\'s always beneficial to test yourself, but you should not apply for a course if you feel you\'re in a bind. It\'s not a good idea to end backward and regret your program choice.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_6d5zasqwxi9k\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">What skills and experience do you hold?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Most university programs outline the subjects you must study and the grade you should earn if you wish to be accepted into a university.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Make a list of all the subjects you\'re studying at the moment and research the kinds of courses you\'ll be prepared for. Examine the requirements for grades and then compare them to the qualities you\'re expecting to earn.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">It\'s crucial to be a realist. If you\'re not going to earn the grades you\'re looking for, try searching for a comparable program with more minor admission requirements. There are thousands of options available, and you shouldn\'t be concerned when you don\'t find the right one-to-one match.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_9iqix875igu\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">What would you like your course to cover?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Although many courses are given the identical name, the content of each course can differ dramatically. Before making your application make sure you spend time studying descriptions of the curriculum and the subjects, you\'ll be learning. Always be sure that the courses you choose are interesting and in line with your passions.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">It is also advisable to consider the extra opportunities that are offered in the programs as well. For example, guest lectures, industry placements, and study abroad options might influence your choice.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">Ask for help</span></strong></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Selecting a college will be among your most crucial choices for an international scholar. Fortunately, your family members, friends, teachers, and career advisors are an excellent source of encouragement and support. They are aware of what you like and what you excel at, which is why they can help you choose the best program.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Don\'t forget to mention us. Our friendly students\' support staff can assist you with any questions you may have. So don\'t hesitate to reach us.</span></p>', '1727869092_IGC-study-Abroad (4).png', '1', '2024-10-02 11:38:12', '2024-10-02 11:38:12', NULL),
(10, 7, '2024-10-02', 'How to make your study abroad journey smooth with IGC: Impact Global Consultant?', 'how-to-make-your-study-abroad-journey-smooth-with-igc:-impact-global-consultant?', 'Here’s some helpful advice from Impact Global Consultant (IGC) on how to get prepared as you plan your studies abroad', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Here&rsquo;s some helpful advice from</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">Impact Global Consultant (IGC)</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"> on how to get prepared as you plan your studies abroad. You&rsquo;ve made the excellent choice to study abroad. So, what&rsquo;s your next move?</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">How do you plan your journey?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Studying abroad can be challenging at times, but it can also be one of the most pleasing, lifetime experiences of your life. We know exactly how worthwhile it can be and how you can avoid the complications that might stand in your higher study.<br>Reading the content, you will have a clear idea of making your study abroad journey as smooth as possible.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_j5r8bqwv2e76\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Collect All the Essential Documents</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Before studying abroad, prepare all the documents you&rsquo;ll need to apply to the university. This list will likely include:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Passport<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Your passport should expire no sooner than six months after the end of your study abroad term. Therefore, make sure that there is an extra page on your passport. You don&rsquo;t want to run into passport problems when you&rsquo;re abroad.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Academic Certificate<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Contact your university to collect your academic transcript, testimonial, and certificate. If possible, collect Medium of Instruction (MoI). Also, you can contact your university teachers to get recommendations from them. And ensure that they will send the recommendation to the university on time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">English language certificate<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">If possible, take the IELTS exam and secure a good score, allowing you to admit into most renowned universities or colleges. However, if you are afraid of IELTS, you can take the Duolingo test, which will save you time, money, and effort; compared to IELTS. If any of the two is not possible, you can admit into a university with MoI or contact the university for an internal English test. Lastly, you can apply with ESL courses if any of these options are not possible for you.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_bum3tgb2x8cv\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Where should you study abroad?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">If you want to study abroad in university or college programs, find out it matches your previous education. This is the easiest way for you when accepted by the university or college. On the other hand, if you want to enhance your professional skills, the degree should match your professional experience and build a solid connection to why completing this course will secure a better career outcome.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Keep track of your finances</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Studying abroad is expensive. Everyone cannot afford it. Therefore, you must calculate all the expenses prior. Most importantly, create an account in your name or your sponsor&rsquo;s name (parents, brothers, or close blood relatives) and maintain a sufficient amount of money covering at least first-year education and living expenses. Alongside, prepare all the legal documents such as Tax Certificate, Bank Solvency Certificate, Land Papers, and Deeds.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Next, prepare a budget, and if you haven&rsquo;t already applied for financial help, continue applying for student loans, scholarships, and any other financial facility you qualify for.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Scholarships and Assistance<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Numbers of universities worldwide offer international student scholarships. If you keep an eye on Scholarship Positions, you will find numerous scholarships available where you can apply. Also, you can inquire about the scholarship at particular universities as well. And you can Google it by typing &ldquo;scholarships for Bangladeshi students,&rdquo; thereby you can see what scholarships are available.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Prepare your mindset to live alone<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">In a foreign country, you will be alone for a long time. All face homesickness as students land in a foreign country. Consequently, they wish to come back to the country. If you don&rsquo;t want this to happen to you, I suggest you try to do all your daily chores, such as cooking, laundry, shopping, and driving by yourself. Especially, change your mindset to live alone and take care of yourself like you are all your own.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Travel around Bangladesh<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">As a student, you must travel now and then to navigate and explore Bangladesh. Traveling will allow you to cope with the new situation and make you aware of the diverse customs, foods, and transportation. Thereby, you will be accustomed to change, and you will feel comfortable while studying abroad.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Draw a Career Roadmap<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">The last but not the least fact you should consider is writing your career outcome articulately if you wish to study abroad. A solid plan will lead you to achieve the best in your life after completing your study. Try to consider your passion, education, experience, and course that you are studying to fix your career roadmap. Several options may come, but choose your options wisely; take some time to set your career goal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Conclusion<br></span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">With that said, IGC teams wish you should have no trouble if you precisely follow the list; best of luck!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Impact Global Consultant is an overseas consultancy that can help you organize your education abroad in the best way possible. We help students to plan their overseas study journey smoothly and affordably. If you have any queries, please call or WhatsApp us at +880 1681-462212</span></p>', '1727869511_How-to-make-your-study-abroad-journey-smooth.png', '1', '2024-10-02 11:45:11', '2024-10-02 11:45:11', NULL);
