(11, 8, '2024-10-02', 'IELTS Speaking-Common Mistakes', 'ielts-speaking-common-mistakes', 'There are some common mistakes we make during the IELTS speaking exam which results in a poor score', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>IELTS Speaking-Common Mistakes </span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">There are some common mistakes we make during the IELTS speaking exam which results in a poor score. Today we\'ll talk about such a</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">common mistake.</span></a></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_x29nqwrypnhp\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">**𝐃𝐎𝐍\'𝐓 𝐌𝐄𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐈𝐙𝐄!</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">A lot of us have the tendency to memorize the most common questions like talk \'about your family\' or \'talk about your hobbies\' etc. It is true that if we memorize the answers, we feel more confident within ourselves about that particular question.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">But, the problem with memorizing is, while talking about memorized contents, we give out quite a robotic and bland expression. That makes us look less/ill prepared in front of the instructor. Since this his job to asses us and he have been doing that job for years, he/she can easily identify our memorized questions and this will always result in a poor score.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">So our tip for you is,</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_5wju22levun1\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">𝐍𝐄𝐕𝐄𝐑 𝐌𝐄𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐈𝐙𝐄 𝐀𝐍𝐘𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐍𝐆!</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Always try to speak naturally and spontaneously. Be as fluent as you can be while speaking . And always remember, confidence is and always will be, your best friend.</span></p>', '1727869850_IELTS Speaking Common Mistakes.png', '1', '2024-10-02 11:50:50', '2024-10-02 11:50:50', NULL),
(12, 9, '2024-10-02', 'Canada-UK Application Day', 'canada-uk-application-day', 'Are you aspiring to study at one of the top-ranked universities in the CANADA or UK?', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Canada-UK Application Day</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Date: 21 January 2023<br>Venue: IGC Office-2/2, Block:A, Lalmatia, Dhaka-1207<br><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><br>Dear students,<br>Are you aspiring to study at one of the top-ranked universities in the</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/study-in-canada/2\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/study-in-canada/2\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">CANADA or UK?<br></span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Here is some Great News for you!<br>We\'re going to host an 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐃𝐚𝐲 session and the session will take place on 21 January 2023 at 𝐈𝐆𝐂 𝐎𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐜𝐞: 2/2, Block: A, Lalmatia, Dhaka-1207<br></span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/cwW3WYZ9T977bCFd8\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; fon