(13, 6, '2024-10-02', '𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐥𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐬𝐞𝐧𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐲 𝐢𝐧 𝐂𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐝𝐚?', 'w𝐡𝐲-𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐥𝐝-𝐲𝐨𝐮-𝐬𝐞𝐧𝐝-𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫-𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐝-𝐭𝐨-𝐬𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐲-𝐢𝐧-c𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐝𝐚?', 'The key advantages of a Canada student visa for children include the ability for parents to physically accompany their child and take care of them', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">𝐖𝐡𝐲<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐥𝐝 𝐬𝐞𝐧𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐲 𝐢𝐧 𝐂𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐝𝐚?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">The key advantages of a Canada student visa for children include the ability for parents to physically accompany their child and take care of them, a potential immigration path, and world-class educational facilities, among other things. Canadian students who complete high school are accepted automatically into any of the country\'s excellent universities. In order to pursue further education, such as a Bachelor\'s degree, the student is not required to return to their place of origin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">It is and always has been a top option for students from other countries. Canada is a safe and peaceful country with a stable government. Canadian degrees are respected around the world, and the country\'s healthcare system is among the best in the world. As a cosmopolitan society that holds that all people should have access to quality education, it has traditionally welcomed students from all over the world.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_ppan2qqx6trk\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">𝐅𝐢𝐧𝐝 𝐚</span></strong><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/study-in-canada/2\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></strong></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/study-in-canada/2\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">𝐒𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐨𝐥 𝐢𝐧 𝐂𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐝𝐚</span></strong></a></span></h2>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">Many Canadian elementary and senior schools welcome students from other countries. Yet, most Bangladeshi families want their children to attend schools in Toronto. Public schools in the Toronto District School Board (TDSB) and other highly regarded private schools in the city </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">are highly sought after by international students. The following are the 15 best schools in Toronto, Ontario, Canada, for elementary and secondary education.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">1. TDSB &ndash; Albert Campbell Collegiate Institute</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">2. TDSB &ndash; Central Toronto Academy</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">3. TDSB &ndash; Forest Hill Collegiate Institute</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">4. TDSB &ndash; Monarch Park Collegiate Institute</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">5. TDSB &ndash; Western Technical-Commercial School</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">6. Toronto International College</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Robot