(17, 10, '2024-10-03', 'Business Degrees in Finnish Universities as a Bangladeshi Student', 'business-degrees-in-finnish-universities-as-a-bangladeshi-student', 'Higher Horizons: Pursuing STEM and STEM-Related Business Degrees in Finnish Universities as a Bangladeshi Student', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Higher Horizons: Pursuing STEM and STEM-Related Business Degrees in Finnish Universities as a Bangladeshi Student</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">The pursuit of higher education marks a pivotal juncture in an individual\'s life, opening doors to a world of possibilities and shaping one\'s future trajectory. For Bangladeshi students with an aptitude for science and business, venturing abroad for higher education presents an exceptional opportunity to broaden their horizons, gain </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">international exposure, and acquire globally recognized qualifications.</span><span lang=\"EN\"><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/Study-in-Finland/6\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"> </span></a><a href=\"https://igc.com.bd/country/Study-in-Finland/6\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #1155cc;\">Finland,</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"> with its world-class universities, innovative research culture, and thriving STEM ecosystem, emerges as a compelling destination for Bangladeshi students seeking to excel in STEM and STEM-related business fields.</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_ytc18awjbuec\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 23.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Why Choose Higher Education Abroad?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Stepping beyond the familiar shores of Bangladesh to pursue higher education abroad offers a multitude of benefits that can significantly enrich one\'s academic and personal growth. Embracing the global stage of education provides access to a wider range of specialized programs, allowing students to delve into their chosen fields with greater depth and focus. Exposure to diverse perspectives, teaching methodologies, and cultural nuances fosters a well-rounded understanding of the subject matter, preparing students for success in an increasingly interconnected world.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 4.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_z911xliljdpr\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 17.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Bangladeshi Students: Well-Equipped for Foreign Education</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Bangladeshi students possess a strong foundation in STEM subjects, stemming from a rigorous secondary education system that emphasizes critical thinking, problem-solving, and analytical skills. Their innate intellectual curiosity and resilience, coupled with a growing emphasis on English language proficiency, make them well-equipped to adapt to the demands of foreign education systems.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 14.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; page-break-after: auto;\"><a name=\"_t6igjxsg25no\"></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Finland: A Haven for STEM Excellence</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Finland\'s reputation as a global leader in STEM education is well-deserved. The country\'s universities consistently rank among the top in the world, offering a comprehensive range of STEM programs at both the bachelor\'s and master\'s levels. These programs are renowned for their emphasis on research, innovation, and practical application, preparing graduates for successful careers in industry and academia.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Quality Education at Affordable Costs</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">A key factor in selecting a study destination is the cost of education. While private universities in Bangladesh can be expensive, pursuing a STEM degree in Finland proves to be a more economical choice. Tuition fees for international students at Finnish universities are relatively affordable, and the country\'s living costs are comparable to those in major cities around the world.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Living Standards and Post-Study Work Opportunities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Finland offers a high standard of living, characterized by a safe and secure environment, quality healthcare, and a commitment to sustainability. The country\'s strong economy and thriving tech sector provide ample opportunities for graduates to secure employment upon completion of their studies.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Degree Recognition and Quality of Life</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Degrees earned from Finnish universities are recognized globally, opening doors to career opportunities worldwide. Moreover, Finland consistently ranks among the top countries in terms of overall quality of life, offering a harmonious blend of work-life balance, cultural attractions, and natural beauty.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Research-Based Master\'s Programs for Global Recognition</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">For Bangladeshi students seeking to pursue research-based master\'s programs, Finland provides an ideal environment for scholarly advancement. Finnish universities are at the forefront of scientific research, with a strong emphasis on collaboration and innovation. Master\'s programs in Finland are designed to nurture critical thinking, research skills, and the ability to contribute to the global scientific community.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Global Rankings of Finnish Universities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Finland\'s commitment to quality education is reflected in the impressive rankings of its universities. According to the Academic Ranking of World Universities (ARWU), three Finnish universities &ndash; the University of Helsinki, Aalto University, and the University of Turku &ndash; rank among the top 100 in the world. Additionally, the Times Higher Education (THE) World University Rankings place three Finnish universities &ndash; Aalto University, the University of Helsinki, and the University of Turku &ndash; within the top 200.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">6. Unveiling the Top Finnish Universities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">Finland boasts a remarkable collection of universities, each offering a unique academic experience and contributing to the country\'s reputation for excellence in higher education. Here\'s a glimpse into the top Finnish universities that consistently shine in global rankings:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\">University of Helsinki:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529;\"> Established in 1640, the University of Helsinki stands as Finland\'s oldest and largest university, renowned for its comprehensive range of academic programs and its strong research focus.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; mso-fareast-font-family: Roboto; mso-bidi-font-family: Roboto; color: #212529; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><!-- [if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"image4.jpg\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\r\n alt=\"Image of University of Helsinki Main Building\" style=\'width:187.8pt;\r\n height:150pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\'>\r\n <v:imagedata