(26, 'AHSAN HABIB TALHA', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Managing Director</span></p>', '+8801681462212', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Hello,</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">I want to convey to you all a word about the value of ongoing learning and self-improvement in my capacity as managing director of our education consulting business. It\'s essential for us to keep up with the most recent industry trends and best practices given the constantly changing nature of education and advising. This implies that we must be dedicated to continuing our schooling and developing as professionals. I urge each and every one of you to take advantage of the various learning opportunities available to you, whether it be through attending workshops and conferences, taking part in online courses, or simply reading industry publications and staying informed.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Additionally, I think that our clients anticipate that we will be subject matter experts in our industry and have a thorough grasp of the difficulties and opportunities that the education sector faces. By making an investment in our own education and professional growth, we not only broaden our own knowledge and skill sets but also raise the value we deliver to our customers.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">So let\'s resolve to our own development and learning and work hard to constantly get better as people and as a business.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">I\'m grateful.</span><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Best regards,</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Ahsan Habib Talha</span></p>