(27, 'Masum Billah', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Chief Executive Officer-CEO</span></p>', '+8801913754152', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Hi,</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">As the Chief Executive Officer of our education consulting firm, I wanted to take a minute to share a message with all of you. Prior to anything else, I want to thank each and every one of you for your effort and commitment to our company. We have developed into one of the top consulting companies for education in the market as a result of your dedication to greatness. I also want to acknowledge that as a company, we should constantly be looking for methods to advance and expand. This means that we must resist the temptation to rest on our laurels in the face of our present success and instead push ourselves to come up with fresh, cutting-edge approaches to serving our customers. I\'ve made a commitment to spending money on our team\'s education and growth as a whole as business president. We will encourage you to pursue additional educational opportunities that can help you develop both personally and professionally, as well as training and resources to help you stay current on industry trends and best practices. I strongly believe that when we invest in our own education, we not only advance our own skills and knowledge but also increase the value we provide to the clientele and the company as a whole.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">So let\'s continue to collaborate to improve our school consulting business. We can make sure that we stay at the forefront of the industry and continue to provide our clients with exceptional service by placing a high priority on our own education and growth. I appreciate your effort and commitment, and I look forward to working with you all in the future to accomplish even greater success.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n